<span id="Architectural_design"></span>
== Progettazione architettonica ==

Videos that go through modeling of rooms, houses, office buildings, and similar structures, and drawing floor plans, using workbenches such as [[Image:Workbench_Draft.svg|24px]] [[Draft_Workbench|Draft]] and [[Image:Workbench_BIM.svg|24px]] [[BIM_Workbench|BIM]].

Since there are many videos that deal with this topic, please visit [[Video_tutorials_for_architectural_design|Video tutorials for architectural design]].

== Finite element (FEM) simulation ==

* [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wAJe1R5NDGw FreeCAD FEM/Civil/Structural/Arch Tutorial-1-An Introduction]: FreeCAD 0.16, and introduction that builds a simple structure of pillars and beams, and analyzes them with the [[Image:Workbench_FEM.svg|24px]] [[FEM Workbench|FEM Workbench]], by Eklavya Self Learning Tutorials.

* [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dhrynRdBOIg How To Use FreeCAD FEM] [12:15] FreeCAD v0.19, Intro to using the FEM workbench. Very well done, by Joko Engineering

* [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qWtMJagDoRk FreeCAD FEM VS SolidWorks FEA Simulation - How Do They Compare?] [12:22] - A side-by-side comparison of FreeCAD 0.19.x FEM and Solidworks 2017 FEA, by Joko Engineering

